<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <meta name="description" content="FROGZ: The open-source, anti-bloat microhosting service for simple, private, and ad-free webpages. Create your internet presence. Introducing The FrogPost for private, E2E encrypted messages.">
  <title>FROGZ - Anti-Bloat Web Services</title>

  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/basic.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/frontpage.css">

  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.png">
</head>

<body>
  <main class="frontpage-main">
    <header class="hero-section">
      <h1 class="shimmer title">FROGZ</h1>
      <div class="flipper-container">
        <img src="/apu_band.gif" alt="A group of frogs playing musical instruments" class="main-hero-image">
      </div>
      <p class="tagline"><i>Your destination for <strong>anti-bloat web services</strong> â€“ simple, private, and free.</i></p>
    </header>

    <section class="intro-section content-box">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Welcome to the Lean Web.</h2>
      <p>In an internet dominated by complexity and tracking, <strong>FROGZ</strong> offers a radical alternative. We champion <strong>simplicity, privacy, and user control</strong>, staunchly opposing the "soydev" trend of bloated web services.</p>

      <div class="service-highlight">
        <h3><span class="service-icon pages-icon"></span> <strong>FROGZ Web Pages</strong></h3>
        <p>Create your own internet presence using just <strong>plain text</strong>, <strong>HTML</strong>, or even <strong>Markdown</strong>. Absolutely no registration required, no ads, and no client-side JavaScript on your published pages.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="service-highlight">
        <h3><span class="service-icon mailbox-icon"></span> <strong>The FrogPost</strong></h3>
        <p>Receive <strong>anonymous, end-to-end encrypted messages</strong> without email. Set up a private inbox, share its public link, and check for messages that automatically expire after one week. Total privacy for both sender and receiver.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="action-section content-box">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Get Started Today</h2>
      <div class="action-buttons-grid">
        <div class="action-card">
          <img src="/pages.png" alt="Frogz Pages icon" class="action-icon">
          <a href="/new" class="action-link">Create a FROGZ Page</a>
        </div>
        <div class="action-card">
          <img src="/mailbox.png" alt="FrogPost icon" class="action-icon">
          <a href="/inbox/create" class="action-link">Create Your Anonymous Inbox</a>
        </div>
        <div class="action-card">
          <img src="/sherlock.png" alt="Frog detective icon" class="action-icon">
          <a href="/random" class="action-link">Explore a Random FROGZ Page</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="main-separator">

    <section class="info-features-grid content-box">
      <div class="info-section">
        <h2 class="section-heading">More Info</h2>
        <ul class="info-list">
          <li><a href="/news">News</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about">About Us</a></li>
          <li><a href="/terms">Terms &amp; Conditions</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="features-section">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Why FROGZ & FrogPost?</h2>
        <ul class="features-list">
          <li>Absolutely <strong>FREE</strong> and <strong>NO ADS</strong> (ever).</li>
          <li>Totally <strong>anonymous</strong> - no accounts, no tracking.</li>
          <li>Your data, your control - designed for <strong>privacy</strong>.</li>
          <li><strong>Open-Source</strong> (AGPL3.0) and open to contributions.</li>
          <li>Built to be <strong>bloat-free</strong> and lightning fast.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
